feat: stop button for conversations. Red square button replaces send button while agent is responding. POST /conversations/{id}/stop sets processing_status to idle and marks messages processed. The processor's process_loop now checks is_processing() at the top of each iteration — when it sees idle, it breaks out of the loop. Frontend cancels the SSE subscription and resets sending/thinking state. This is a soft stop — it won't kill an in-flight harness call, but it prevents the processor from sending the next message.
